node.text:
Today is my last day on the #connectingeurope express train. I've stayed in a different European city every day for 10 days in a row and saw many in between. I loved exploring them all. I also like modern cities, like this collection that has images from Hong Kong, Dubai, Busan and Seoul.
.
Thank you all for following my trip through my stories. I have many images from different cities I have to work in, so you'll see some of that content soon.
.
#traveleurope #discoverEU #moderncities #burjkhalifa #mydubailife #hongkongphotography #cityskyline #amazingcities #skyscraping_architecture

node.text:
I'm still in Italy and yesterday we crossed Tuscany and Cinque Terre with the #connectingeurope express. It was especially great to see the hills of Tuscany outside the train window. I took this collection of Tuscany images on an earlier visit. I am currently in Rome and will move to Bolzano this afternoon.
.
#EUYearofRail #DiscoverEU #traveleurope 
.
#italygram #ig_italia #loveitaly #toscana #tuscanygram #tuscanyitaly #tuscanylovers

node.text:
I am currently crossing Italy with the #connectingeurope express train. first stop was Turin, then Milano and today we are going to Rome. Italy has so much variety in landscapes and cities. The Dolomites is one of my favourites especially in autumn. The colours of the trees are simply incredible then.
.
#EUYearofRail #DiscoverEU #traveleurope

node.text:
I woke up in Madrid, Spain yesterday morning, slept in Bordeaux France last night and arriving in Turin Italy today. I'm traveling by train through Europe with the #connectingeurope express. 
.
Italy is one of my favourite countries in Europe. They just have so much beauty there. I love the little villages along the coast. These photos are from Cinque Terre. The villages of Cinque Terre are connected by train that goes through tunnels in the rocks, making it possible to go from village to village in a very short time.
.
#cinqueterre #loveitaly #italytravel #italygram #ig_italia #italytrip #coastalliving #beautifultown #beautifulvillage #italy_vacations #cinqueterreitaly #traveleurope #discovereu

node.text:
While I'm sitting on the #connectingeurope express train this week and looking out of the window dreaming away from all the different landscapes I see passing by, the first little mushrooms are already popping out of the ground when the forests are wet. With September just started the first signs of autumn can already be seen in some parts of Europe.
.
#discovereu #mushrooms_of_our_world #mushroomspotting #mushroomseason #macrophotography #macroworld #macro_kings #macronature #macramelove

node.text:
The upcoming days I am crossing Europe by train with the #connectingeuropeexpress . This year is the Year of Rail. Using train travel is comfortable and sustainable. The CEE crosses 26 countries in 36 days. I will be in different countries and cities almost every day. It also crosses my hometown Amsterdam, to be seen in this collection. Follow my stories in the upcoming 9 days to see where the trains will take me. I'll also explain how easy it is to travel by train through Europe, how to find the nice spots, how to plan and much more :)
.
#euyearofrail #traveleurope #discovereu #disovereurope #traintravel #amsterdamcity #amsterdamview #amsterdamvibe #livinginamsterdam #visitamsterdam #amsterdamworld #sonyalpha
